aws of other countries. Please refer to the organization that has made the Item available for more information.</span><br/>"]}},"navDate":"1815-01-27T12:25:59Z","thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/collections/islandora/object/tdh%3A8335/datastream/TN","width":200,"height":200,"type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg"}],"items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/0","type":"Canvas","label":{"none":[" : page 1"]},"width":3321,"height":3957,"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8339~datastream~JP2/full/415,495/0/default.jpg","width":415,"height":495,"type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","service":[{"@id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8339~datastream~JP2","@type":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/context.json","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/level2.json"}]}],"items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/0/page/tdh:8339","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/0/page/tdh:8339/656b68ab3aa70","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","body":{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8339~datastream~JP2/full/full/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","width":3321,"height":3957,"format":"image/jpeg","service":[{"@id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8339~datastream~JP2","@type":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/context.json","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/level2.json"}]},"target":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/0"}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/0/annopage-0","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/0/annopage-0/annotation-0","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":{"type":"TextualBody","language":"en","format":"text/plain","value":"Crabstick 27th January 1815 Dr Dear . Brother Yesterday I received your letter of the 11th instant. The news which it contained I had heard but a little time before, tho though I had anticipated some good news for I actually heard the detail, as the day before I heard such at this place, the sound of cannon fired in rejocing rejoicing at Nashville __ The capture of our Brothers was new to me and to all of your guards men, but I can say they had much same hear they were prisoners than that they had been killed in battle, as in the former case tis hoped a speedy exchange will be affected; and the lattre latter is only preferable to perpetual slavery May I be damned if I had not rather die then become a subject to the King of Great Britain, and I will do it before such a circumstance can take place again business I have incurred little as been & ability would find__ you money I have not been able to collect of Crofton as Wilkerson not yet returned__ Crofton Newman borrowed 30 Dollars opad me for you Your pork I have salted up often paying Powers 10__ Peter 2 & I myself end up making $19 in pork the balance I collect for you about 14 hundred weight"},"target":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/0"}]}],"seeAlso":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/collections/islandora/object/tdh:8339/datastream/HOCR","type":"Dataset","label":{"none":["HOCR"]},"format":"text/vnd.hocr+html","profile":"http://kba.cloud/hocr-spec/1.2/"}]},{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","label":{"none":[" : page 2"]},"width":3320,"height":3915,"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8338~datastream~JP2/full/415,489/0/default.jpg","width":415,"height":489,"type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","service":[{"@id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8338~datastream~JP2","@type":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/context.json","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/level2.json"}]}],"items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/1/page/tdh:8338","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/1/page/tdh:8338/656b68ac74033","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","body":{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8338~datastream~JP2/full/full/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","width":3320,"height":3915,"format":"image/jpeg","service":[{"@id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8338~datastream~JP2","@type":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/context.json","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/level2.json"}]},"target":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/1"}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/1/annopage-1/annotation-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":{"type":"TextualBody","language":"en","format":"text/plain","value":"your shoats were very small some not weighing more than 30 pounds Susan wasted money to purchase pork I wrote to her to use my money all from her Mother & Hrny I have not heard from her since which time was about Christmas I will close this read by observing your business in this state and give you no uneasiness all is well and shall be so if I can make it As I had not heard from you since your departure from Nashville until by this last mail, I two or three posts ago wrote to General Coffee to you on confirmation of you & Tom Ogleman , perceiving your time was devoted entirely to arms, as the enemy was in sight, and hourly skirmishes with you Should you see Mr. Lewis during your stay in that country try and settle my business with him as cannot find it convenient to pay_ one has note in favor of N.P.H. for the 200 dollars, he having the interest in it for I was not to appropriate to my use any of the earnings of our joint labors in trade, and I know he is more necessitous than I am"},"target":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/1"}]}],"seeAlso":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/collections/islandora/object/tdh:8338/datastream/HOCR","type":"Dataset","label":{"none":["HOCR"]},"format":"text/vnd.hocr+html","profile":"http://kba.cloud/hocr-spec/1.2/"}]},{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/2","type":"Canvas","label":{"none":[" : page 3"]},"width":3253,"height":3926,"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8337~datastream~JP2/full/407,491/0/default.jpg","width":407,"height":491,"type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","service":[{"@id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8337~datastream~JP2","@type":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/context.json","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/level2.json"}]}],"items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/2/page/tdh:8337","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/2/page/tdh:8337/656b68ada1701","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","body":{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8337~datastream~JP2/full/full/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","width":3253,"height":3926,"format":"image/jpeg","service":[{"@id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8337~datastream~JP2","@type":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/context.json","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/level2.json"}]},"target":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/2"}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/2/annopage-2","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/2/annopage-2/annotation-2","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":{"type":"TextualBody","language":"en","format":"text/plain","value":"Let me hear from you as often as convenient though I should not write to you_ Your news will be interesting there is some here & my silence may open you all such as soon as any thing turns out of the ordinary way I shall advise you of it Try and remember what handsome flower seeds you can bring up, and whatever else you may judge I want as a curiosity for my garden Your Brother John Hardeman Peter Hardeman by God you will have hard work to read this_ I asked if Mrs. Sutter and opelent out of sunday Bailey is with me You can see I have named my plantation Crabstick"},"target":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/2"}]}],"seeAlso":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/collections/islandora/object/tdh:8337/datastream/HOCR","type":"Dataset","label":{"none":["HOCR"]},"format":"text/vnd.hocr+html","profile":"http://kba.cloud/hocr-spec/1.2/"}]},{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assemble/manifest/tdh/8335/canvas/3","type":"Canvas","label":{"none":[" : page 4"]},"width":3890,"height":3185,"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8336~datastream~JP2/full/486,398/0/default.jpg","width":486,"height":398,"type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","service":[{"@id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/iiif/2/collections~islandora~object~tdh:8336~datastream~JP2","@type":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/context.json","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/level2.json"}]}],"items":[{"id":"https://digital.lib.utk.edu/notdereferenceable/assembl